Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Nabali-An Elementary School in the Municipality of Himamaylan, Province of Negros Occidental, to Don Marcelo Vasquez Memorial School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 818
An Act Changing the Name of the Nabali-An Elementary School in the Municipality of Himamaylan, Province of Negros Occidental, to Don Marcelo Vasquez Memorial School
Section 1. The name of the Nabali-an Elementary School in the Municipality of Himamaylan, Province of Negros Occidental, is changed to Don Marcelo Vasquez Memorial School.1Ã¢wphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 27, 1984
